list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Started a massive refactor by pulling in my old map generation code, and then started refactoring that, but in the process have begun a full refactor of the codebase

task.summary: Default task
Added a few small bug fixes and language features
Basic high versian stuff is done, and added some new voices from the void articles!
Made the voices from the void stuff look a lot nicer
Fixed a font bug?
More font fixes!
Fixed a small bug with a switch statement
Added a new voices from the Void issue, and some articles to it.
Started working on Traveller Faction stuff
Made corporation stuff
Added the federation flag and set it as the iamge.
Fixed a small bug

Added religions to the faction system, and companies, and fleshed out companies, and creators for those faction types with more to come. Soon to follow is nations and major nations. Then we'll see what comes after that. Probably criminal elements. Companies is forsure the largest at this time though.
Laid the foundation of the headline generator!
Added the basic other group classes and their relevant creators
Added the json data for the various different groups, added their group pages, and some other stuff and expadned the headline generator

Added the code to handle the last two classes of factions, nations and major nations. Also simplified how islands factions are being loaded with a nice generic method (god bless generics) and some updates to the headline system so that is should now use the new factions for its generation of headlines. Now we just need some data!
Started workig on grtafting in faction assets
Started work on adding faction assets
Added a void news article regarding the death of Matt Warde
overhauled the faction creator pages so that they now work. Just need to finish updating the faction services so that all their home worlds are registered properly.
More fixes! still need to readd the faction data tho
Some final overhauls to the faciton system, the basics of faction assets added, and some more void news stories!
Added two new voices from the void articles, and patched a small bug.
A small bug allowing companies to now have employees
Made the assets now just display locations, and added more islands to Islands.json
Added more Islands
Added some new void news articles, as well as the basics for a basic fantasy RP charactrer creeator
Added hte new voices of the void article
Okay this might finally have fixed it.
Fixed the date on voics from the void
Added some words to high versian and made the pages for it easier to use
Hopefully fixes a bug
Another bug fix, this time related to the links for the lists of pre/root/postfixes

Added a Simple High Versian to English Concept Translator, will add english to high versian maybe probably not at some point.
